# Customer demo recommendation:
# Use a Supabase cloud/staging project so a real Android phone can reach the backend.
# Local Supabase is useful for development, but phones may not reliably reach laptop localhost.
# Never put SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY or SUPABASE_DB_PASSWORD in Expo public env.
#
# Optional local-only values for scripts/create-demo-auth-users.mjs:
# SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key
